  ('chongqing_eling_2nd_factory_sa_02', 'chongqing_eling_2nd_factory', 'Factory II Memory Museum', '二厂记忆博物馆', 'Housed in the original 8-metre-high brick hall of Building 5, the museum exhibits intaglio printing presses, numbering machines and engraved plates from the 1930s Central Bank Printing Works, plus a section on Chongqing''s wartime industrial history. Free admission.

