  ('chongqing_eling_2nd_factory_sa_14', 'chongqing_eling_2nd_factory', 'Hello Childhood Nostalgia Museum', '你好童年怀旧馆', 'An 800 sqm immersive nostalgia museum with thousands of 1970s–90s Chinese objects—enamel mugs, tin frogs, glass marbles, cassette games, and a recreated 1980s classroom with chalkboard desks.

