  ('chongqing_guanyinqiao_sa_01', 'chongqing_guanyinqiao', 'Guanyinqiao Pedestrian Street Plaza', '观音桥步行街广场', 'Covering 58,000 sqm, the plaza was created during the 2003 redevelopment and now welcomes 150 million visitors a year. It links 10+ shopping malls, two metro lines and the central "Jinjie" underground street.

