  ('chongqing_guanyinqiao_sa_02', 'chongqing_guanyinqiao', 'Maoye Tiandi Naked-Eye 3D Screen', '茂业天地"裸眼 3D"大屏', 'A 700 sqm curved P3 LED screen on Maoye Tiandi''s façade, lit in January 2021, displaying "Cyber Chongqing" 3D animations. It is one of the most photographed night attractions in the CBD.

