  ('chongqing_guanyinqiao_sa_03', 'chongqing_guanyinqiao', 'Guanyinqiao Sculpture (City Landmark)', '观音桥雕塑（城市标志）', 'The 16.8 m stainless-steel sculpture with its "Guanyin praying" figure and Chongqing landscape base was unveiled in 2003, refurbished in 2018 and has become the central photo landmark of the CBD.

