  ('chongqing_guanyinqiao_sa_04', 'chongqing_guanyinqiao', 'Beicheng Tianjie (North City Mall)', '北城天街', 'A 380,000 sqm shopping complex opened by Longfor in 2003, comprising Blocks A, B, C (Starlight 68) and X. It houses luxury brands, fashion, dining and entertainment, and is the CBD''s flagship mall.

