：① 3 /9 3 B ；②；③ 30 / (1) Metro Lines 3/9 Guanyinqiao Station Exit 3 direct to Block B; (2) Bus to Beicheng Tianjie/Guanyinqiao; (3) ~30-min taxi from Jiangbei Airport', 'https://edwvrriuwzaaqznklrgi.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/cover-images/sub-areas/all/chongqing_guanyinqiao_sa_04.jpg', 3),
  ('chongqing_guanyinqiao_sa_05', 'chongqing_guanyinqiao', 'Guanyinqiao Jiugie (Sleepless Jiugie - Terminal)', '观音桥九街（不夜九街 - 终点）', 'A 1.2 km nightlife zone with 200+ bars, live houses and 24 h eateries, opened as a pilot "night-economy district" in 2017. Open from 20:00 to 04:00, it is the after-dark terminal of the route.

